- No Jinja parsing required

#### **Layer 2: Specialized Jinja Templates (chat.cpp)**
- Used when templates are complex and need custom parsing logic
- Built-in Jinja execution + PEG parser generation
- For models with special requirements (reasoning, tool calls, etc.)

